snippet.title: Resistor - Official Trailer | Day of the Devs The Game Awards Edition 2023
snippet.description:
Resistor is a narrative-driven adventure racing RPG developed by Long Way Home. Players will go on a journey to save their mother by doing the one thing they swore off but must return to nonetheless. Race against other competitors to reach the top of the podium in this twisting story to take down an oppressive mega-corporation and its enigmatic director. Resistor is PlayStation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch, and PC.

#IGN #Gaming #Resistor
